      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PATIENCE (6) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (25.75) at Ballarat over 450m. Expected to feature in the finish again. MEPUNGA ENVY (8) is a Jeffrey Britton-trained newcomer by Fernando Bale out of Mepunga Isla with no trial form to work with. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability. FLEX FACTOR (7) has been freshened since missing the frame on debut at Healesville over 350m (20.07). Expected to do much better this time. GLIMMERING (3) can fill a top-three spot.",
